## 3. Dataset Description

The dataset contains information related to online orders including:

| Feature | Description |
|----------|------------|
| Date | Order Date |
| Quantity | Number of Items Purchased |
| UnitPrice | Price per Unit |
| TotalPrice | Total Order Value |
| CouponCode | Applied Discount Coupon |
| PaymentMethod | Payment Mode |
| OrderStatus | Delivery Status |
| ReferralSource | Source of Customer |
| ItemsInCart | Number of Items in Cart |

